2. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) - The paper discusses the construction and analysis of a network, which falls under the scope of networking and internet architecture. 
3. cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) - The paper deals with a network with multiple sources and terminals, which can be considered a social and information network. 
4. cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) - The paper describes a procedure for constructing a sum-network using an undirected graph, which involves algorithms and data structures. 
5. cs.CC (Computational Complexity) - The paper discusses the computation rate and capacity analysis of a network, which can be considered a problem in computational complexity.
